:: 怡安小区 [location]
<<setmap "怡安小区">><<location "怡安小区">><<mode "location">>

<div id="append-text" class="append-normal"></div>
<div id="situation" class="situation">
<<you>>站在公寓楼前，在手机上查看景南市的地图，思考着接下来去哪里。<br>
</div>

<br>
<<if $Flag.interactionlock isnot true>>
<div class="tolink">
